item.title: Adidas Brings Back Classic Trefoil Logo on Third Kits for 5 Elite European Clubs

item.title: Rollin’ on the River: USL’s Memphis 901 FC Launch Alternate Jersey
item.description: Kits honors founding of Memphis along the bluffs of the Mississippi River; club will donate 10% of jersey sales to non-profit helping kids fight cancer

item.title: Las Vegas Raiders Honor Late Hall Of Famer Jim Otto With Helmet Decal
item.description: The Las Vegas Raiders have added a decal to the back of their helmets in honor of late Hall of Fame center Jim Otto, who passed away in May at the age of 86.
